data.title: Samreen Mirza - Hyderabad, PressMart Media Ltd, Bachelor in Computer Science
data.text: Sr Android Developer open to tasks that challenge my talent and my time management. I feel Java as a novel Eclispse as my drawing board where I will sketch my own world of apps from the thoughts kicked off through my java novel .... So thats what I am after 2 yrs of my journey in Java and hope this novel gives alot more to do on this drawing board in coming future
